{"tid":1446010,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 全民流動文宣","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:00:22.000Z","uid":44312,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"294036e426caef97ed427369ef5ff2aa97c1462f","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:40:10.000Z","msg":"宜家文宣好大問題係只接觸到同溫層<br />\n睇新聞睇到好嬲但好多港豬比cctvb洗腦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>建議大家聽日開始喺袋或者身上掛文宣材料</strong><br />\n迫啲港豬平時行街返工買餸都見到<br />\n<br />\n文宣材料可以有以下特點<br />\n1. 非同溫層自high文宣<br />\n2. 比較多資訊，唔好得句口號<br />\n3. 有cctvb無既資訊，例如黑警暴行，警黑合作，林鄭既大話<br />\n4. 有截圖吸引注意同證實係事實<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家繼續拋磚引玉"},{"pid":"86d5fc7110540a2d71d579ee74afcc1fb18c5418","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"915508d399eff6ad169bb8ad6d4485602bf40f9a","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9be42c88c2d4869ad948ed4bdadfe70b04479d8d","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:51:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"233ca760ba1bd564e932bec71d547725d208e26c","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9542b9b4176f5570a82b4aa9ed3754988f821c48","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:53:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b85a21171ded67b72f7e008a309c8ed948cacf91","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30c217fa3ea4c17e52eff5f09b07c130c660cc79","tid":1446010,"uid":44312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:00:06.000Z","msg":"要打輿論戰呀<br />\n和理非做野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces